<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="page-header page-header-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>About Greymatter Accountancy</h1>
        <p>Intelligent accounting for London's ambitious businesses</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-page">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-section">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Gray Matter Accountancy was founded on a simple belief: accounting should make life easier, not more
            complicated.

            We know business owners have enough on their plates without worrying about accounts, tax, and compliance.
            That’s why we’re here — to take the burden off your shoulders and give you more time to focus on growing
            your business.

            You focus on what you do best. We’ll take care of the numbers.</p>
          <p>We work with ambitious businesses across different stages and sectors. Every client relationship is built
            on deep understanding and genuine commercial insight.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
          <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
          <p><strong>Grey Matter</strong> — the substance of intelligence. We apply rigorous analytical thinking to
            every engagement, solving complex accounting challenges with commercial pragmatism.</p>
          <div class="philosophy-points">
            <div class="philosophy-card">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Think Differently</h3>
              <p>Every business is unique. We reject templates and apply bespoke thinking to your specific structure and
                challenges.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="philosophy-card">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Partnership Approach</h3>
              <p>We're not just service providers — we're part of your team, invested in your success and available when
                you need us.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="philosophy-card">
              <h3><i class="fas fa-target"></i> Results-Driven</h3>
              <p>Compliance is table-stakes. We focus on tax optimization, strategic insight, and actionable financial
                intelligence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-section">
          <h2>Why Choose Greymatter?</h2>
          <div class="why-cards">
            <div class="why-card">
              <h3>Same-Day Responsiveness</h3>
              <p>Based in London's financial district, we understand the pace of business and respond accordingly. Your
                questions get answered fast.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
              <h3>Technical Care, Bespoke Services</h3>
              <p>We bring structured thinking, careful delivery, and genuine accessibility to our bespoke services.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
              <h3>Industry Specialists</h3>
              <p>Deep expertise in property, tech, creative, professional services, and hospitality. We speak your
                business language.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="why-card">
              <h3>Fixed Pricing, Transparent Fees</h3>
              <p>No surprises. We quote fixed monthly or project fees. Costs are predictable and aligned with service
                delivery.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>



    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to Work with Greymatter?</h2>
        <p>Let's discuss how we can help your business thrive.</p>
        <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>

</html>